        {
            "title": "海關一日內破兩宗旅客販運毒品案 檢$1190萬K仔及可卡因 2女被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/50fca9a29c3c1be1a9ebb8dadae23adf/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250413/_2025041321480614788.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>香港海關昨日（12日）在香港國際機場破獲兩宗涉及旅客販運毒品的案件，檢獲共約12公斤懷疑氯胺酮及約7公斤懷疑可卡因，估計市值共約1190萬元。     <br/>\n<br/>\n首宗案件中，一名19歲本地女子昨日從法國巴黎飛抵本港。海關人員清關時，在其寄艙行李內發現約12公斤懷疑氯胺酮，遂把她拘捕。被捕女子已被控以一項販運危險藥物罪，明日（14日）在西九龍裁判法院提堂。<br/>\n<br/>\n第二宗案件中，海關人員昨日透過風險評估截查一名57歲、準備從本港飛往布魯塞爾的女旅客，並在其寄艙物品內發現約7公斤懷疑可卡因，隨即把她拘捕。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4193350/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"檢獲的懷疑可卡因。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8893f818322eafb083c73f2cd3c1f3e6/2025-04/011F2A7CC1644CB6BBCD8D1AD989C1F7_O.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        檢獲的懷疑可卡因。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4193351/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"檢獲的懷疑氯胺酮。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cb6a4e71d9bb3ad91f0b0df11e63b061/2025-04/F8084BF4001449BA973966D7E4731ED0_O.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        檢獲的懷疑氯胺酮。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2063756/即時-港聞-海關一日內破兩宗旅客販運毒品案-檢-1190萬K仔及可卡因-2女被捕",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-13 22:01:42",
